有唔少朋友 外向social</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n身邊有幾個朋友都係咁 想瞭解返 其實係點解會導致你咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一黎本質比較孤僻 但我(佢地)知點先social到<br />\n二黎可能係朋友方面受過傷害 eg背叛<br />\n所以唔打開個心<br />\n<br />\n但只要你係佢認定值得既人<br />\n而你又夠關心佢 佢就會掏曬心肺<br />\n但呢個人通常係我既另一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dae1dca7a7b2fa19e5b2ab96b1e830fe8eb00b6","tid":129783,"uid":73876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:39:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我。唔係話攰既<br />\n只係唔太需要佢地<br />\n需要佢地既時候係想搵人消磨下時間<br />\n有人wtsapp搵自己 一齊出街食飯去玩<br />\n唔鐘意太親近同頻繁既接觸 <br />\n對朋友呢樣野好無感覺 番到屋企都唔太覆wstapp<br />\n<br />\n不過佢地想傾心事絕對願意聽<br />\n比意見, 安慰 我都想幫到佢地<br />\n<br />\n利申 有唔少朋友 外向social</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n身邊有幾個朋友都係咁 想瞭解返 其實係點解會導致你咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一黎本質比較孤僻 但我(佢地)知點先social到<br />\n二黎可能係朋友方面受過傷害 eg背叛<br />\n所以唔打開個心<br />\n<br />\n但只要你係佢認定值得既人<br />\n而你又夠關心佢 佢就會掏曬心肺<br />\n但呢個人通常係我既另一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我好似係依類人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5871ac26f70e4a27df3c7fc1e5d234e3f5cbb3c1","tid":129783,"uid":87525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:49:57.000Z","msg":"佢地有時比到啲好好既意見你<br />\n但其實佢地都係食花生為主"},{"pid":"4a297a4792b7b9511d2442797caac88a730c965b","tid":129783,"uid":73876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T09:01:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢地有時比到啲好好既意見你<br />\n但其實佢地都係食花生為